note bottom of cgs_core
  **CGS in one sentence:**
  CGS is the municipal service bus that sits between all applications,
  ensuring they can exchange data without knowing each other's protocols,
  formats, or locations. It handles authorization, routing, transformation,
  and delivery — all driven by configuration, not code.
  
  **Scale (this environment):**
  173 registered applications · 220 active services · 660 authorizations
  149 adapters · 532 routing channels · 993 transformations · 2065 message definitions
end note

